[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    232[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mOutcome-capture Lambda fails on a malformed outcome event[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m (the EHR or HIE emits an unexpected outcome-type code, the patient_id references a patient outside the program scope, the linkage fails because of an intermediate-state mismatch). The label is never written; the case never enters the labeled-outcomes archive; the supervised classifier's next retraining run misses the data point; the post-discharge program loses critical positive-class signal.[K
